(AI Practice Bot Project Documentation) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(1. Project Overview) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(AI Practice Bot is a full-stack AI-powered web application for interview preparation. The) Tj T*
(system lets users register, log in, select a job role and difficulty, answer interview) Tj T*
(questions, receive AI-assisted coaching, and save their practice history for review.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(2. Objectives) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(- Provide realistic interview practice for common job roles.) Tj T*
(- Use AI as a core feature for question enhancement, feedback, hints, sample answers,) Tj T*
(follow-up prompts, and session summaries.) Tj T*
(- Store authenticated users' practice sessions in Supabase.) Tj T*
(- Provide a responsive web interface that works on desktop and smaller screens.) Tj T*
(- Prepare the project for public GitHub and Vercel submission.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(3. Scope) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(Included:) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(- User registration, login, logout, email update, and password update.) Tj T*
(- AI-assisted interview practice flow.) Tj T*
(- Saved sessions dashboard, session details, update, and delete actions.) Tj T*
(- Analytics and profile screens.) Tj T*
(- Supabase schema and Row Level Security policies.) Tj T*
(- README and documentation for deployment and evaluation.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(Not included:) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(- Real-time voice transcription.) Tj T*
(- Admin panel for managing all users.) Tj T*
(- Payment or subscription features.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(4. Technology Stack) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(Layer Technology) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(Frontend React, TSX, Vite) Tj T*
(Styling Tailwind CSS) Tj T*
(Backend/Database Supabase Auth and Supabase Postgres) Tj T*
(AI Gemini API) Tj T*
(Deployment Target Vercel) Tj T*
(Version Control Target GitHub public repository) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(5. System Design) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(The app is a Vite single-page React application. The frontend manages the interview) Tj T*
(workflow, calls Gemini for AI coaching, and uses Supabase for authentication and database) Tj T*
(operations.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(High-level flow:) Tj T*
ET
