() Tj T*
(1. User registers or logs in through Supabase Auth.) Tj T*
(2. User chooses role, difficulty, and number of questions.) Tj T*
(3. App prepares local questions and optionally enhances them with Gemini.) Tj T*
(4. User answers questions in a chat-like interface.) Tj T*
(5. App gives local feedback immediately and enhances feedback with Gemini when available.) Tj T*
(6. Completed sessions are saved to Supabase.) Tj T*
(7. User reviews, updates, or deletes saved sessions.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(6. Database Schema) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(sessions) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(Column Type Purpose) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(id uuid Primary key generated by the app) Tj T*
(user_id uuid References auth.users\(id\)) Tj T*
(role text Interview role selected by the user) Tj T*
(difficulty text Easy, Medium, or Hard) Tj T*
(total_score integer Total score for the session) Tj T*
(accuracy integer Percentage score) Tj T*
(followups integer Number of follow-up prompts) Tj T*
(created_at timestamptz Session creation timestamp) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(questions) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(Column Type Purpose) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(id uuid Primary key generated by the app) Tj T*
(session_id uuid References sessions\(id\)) Tj T*
(question text Interview question) Tj T*
(answer text User answer) Tj T*
(score integer Question score) Tj T*
(feedback text Feedback text) Tj T*
(created_at timestamptz Record creation timestamp) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(Row Level Security limits users to their own sessions and related questions.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(7. AI Component Explanation) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(The AI feature is implemented in src/services/geminiService.js. Gemini is used for:) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(- Generating role-specific interview questions.) Tj T*
(- Evaluating candidate answers.) Tj T*
(- Producing follow-up questions when answers are short or vague.) Tj T*
(- Creating hints and topic explanations.) Tj T*
(- Producing sample answers.) Tj T*
(- Summarizing completed interview sessions.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
(The app also has local fallback logic in src/utils/hybridInterview.js so the practice flow) Tj T*
(remains usable if the Gemini API key is missing, rate limited, or temporarily unavailable.) Tj T*
() Tj T*
ET
endstream
